#: ../../../f2py/buildtools/distutils-to-meson.rst:5
msgid "1 Migrating to ``meson``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../f2py/buildtools/distutils-to-meson.rst:7
msgid ""
"As per the timeline laid out in :ref:`distutils-status-migration`, "
"``distutils`` has ceased to be the default build backend for ``f2py``. This "
"page collects common workflows in both formats."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../f2py/buildtools/distutils-to-meson.rst:13
msgid ""
"This is a **living** document, `pull requests <https://numpy.org/doc/stable/"
